The Complete Noob

The Complete Noob is a sourcebook for d20-like systems designed to allow DMs to
add more flavor to low-power NPCs and creatures. It is licensed under CC-BY-SA
(Creative Commons + Attribution + Share-Alike) - see
<http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0>.

You will need a LaTeX renderer to turn the TeX source into a postscript file,
and some way to view postscript files. To find a pre-rendered version of a
recent version of this book, see
<http://www.leptoquark.net/~elly/complete-noob.pdf>.

Enjoy :)
